- describe constraint SOC by SOC, as interrupts of rk3576 is very
  different from others
- Drop Krzysztof's Reviewed-by, as this version changed a lot.

Changes in v3:
- ordered by soc name
- Add description for newly added interrupt

Changes in v2:
- Add dt bindings

